<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CertiFried Announcer - The All-in-One Discord Bot</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/dashboard-style.css?v=4.0.0">
</head>
<body>

<%- include('partials/header-landing') %>

<main class="container">
    <div class="hero">
        <img src="/images/CertiFried.png" alt="Bot Logo" class="hero-logo">
        <h1>CertiFried Announcer</h1>
        <p>The ultimate all-in-one bot for stream announcements, server moderation, and community engagement. Powerful, reliable, and fully customizable.</p>
        <div class="hero-buttons">
            <a href="https://discord.com/api/oauth2/authorize?client_id=<%= client_id %>&permissions=8&scope=bot%20applications.commands" class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" target="_blank">Add to Discord</a>
            <a href="/servers" class="btn btn-lg btn-secondary">Go to Dashboard</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center my-5">
        <h2 class="section-title">A Bot That Does It All</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-broadcast-tower me-2"></i> Multi-Platform Announcements</h3>
            <p>Reliable, real-time notifications for Twitch, YouTube, Kick, and more. Never miss a stream again.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-shield-alt me-2"></i> Powerful Moderation</h3>
            <p>Protect your server with a configurable Automod, Anti-Nuke system, and new member verification.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-tachometer-alt me-2"></i> Web Dashboard</h3>
            <p>Manage every aspect of the bot from a clean, intuitive, and modern web dashboard.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-ticket-alt me-2"></i> Ticket System</h3>
            <p>Provide dedicated support to your members with a fully integrated ticket management tool.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-music me-2"></i> Music Player</h3>
            <p>Play high-quality music directly from YouTube. Manage queues, skip, and stop with simple commands.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-star me-2"></i> And Much More...</h3>
            <p>Includes a leveling system, reaction roles, custom commands, server backups, and invite tracking.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>

<%- include('partials/footer-landing') %>

</body>
</html>